HEADWORD: Ectomere
<hw>Ec"to*mere</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Ecto-</ets> +
<ets>-mere</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>The more transparent
